    <h1>Overnight Oats</h1>

    
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
    
        <li>1 cup rolled oats</li>
    
        <li>1 cup water</li>
    
        <li>1/2 tablespoon chia seeds</li>
    
        <li>1 tablespoon flaxseed meal</li>
    
        <li>10 goji berries</li>
    
        <li>1/2 teaspoon cinnamon</li>
    
    </ul>
    

    
    <h2>Steps</h2>
    <ol>
    
        <li>Add all ingredients to a 1-pint mason jar.</li>
    
        <li>Close the lid.</li>
    
        <li>Shake vigorously for five seconds.</li>
    
        <li>Place in the fridge overnight</li>
    
        <li>Eat the next day (or up to a week later) with sliced banana, frozen blueberries, and/or any combination of fruits on hand.</li>
    
    </ol>
    

    
